oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: TVA's Cherokee Dam on the Holston River, located near Jefferson City, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: TVA's Cherokee Dam. The reservoir behind this dam rose more than 40 ft. during the heavy rains. As soon as possible and after the flood was receding downstream, TVA "sluiced" water from this impoundment to bring the reservoir elevation to a safe level.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dams; Rivers
